{"tid":1263731,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港國歌】商台聽眾合唱團 - 香港之歌 (1969)","createTime":"2019-06-28T10:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:55:40.000Z","uid":35221,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b997b7703fca3c77dd9f26af77d928e1ef22cda","tid":1263731,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qf-hFthH65A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQf-hFthH65A&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=22e5414f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qf-hFthH65A</a><br />\n<br />\n香港之歌 (1969)<br />\n主唱：商台聽眾合唱團 <br />\n作曲：鄺天培<br />\n填詞：鄒方里 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，爐峰輕眺盡遠望， <br />\n萬千氣象，樂滿華堂，繁盛自由更安康。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，民主可貴得眾望， <br />\n外銷工業遐邇名揚，無限貿易流暢。 <br />\n<br />\n處處景致秀麗，大眾喜氣洋洋， <br />\n和平共處，名聞四方，讚賞東方之珠香港。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，民風謙遜重禮讓， <br />\n共享歡樂，大眾安康，愛東方之珠香港。 <br />\n<br />\n南北中西安逸歡暢，同聲頌讚香港， <br />\n勁秀好山城，地老天長，民主之光照香港。 <br />\n<br />\n名昌千秋，聲譽不降，同舟共濟永自強， <br />\n美滿又安寧，是個好天堂，成就是大眾共創。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，爐峰輕眺盡遠望， <br />\n萬千氣象，樂滿華堂，繁盛自由更安康。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，民主可貴得眾望， <br />\n外銷工業遐邇名揚，無限貿易流暢。 <br />\n<br />\n處處景致秀麗，大眾喜氣洋洋， <br />\n和平共處，名聞四方，讚賞東方之珠香港。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，民風謙遜重禮讓， <br />\n共享歡樂，大眾安康，愛東方之珠香港。"},{"pid":"88c54abe1e829dc949091564980e464a2efec7bc","tid":1263731,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"1969年，六七暴動平息冇耐，港英搞咗個香港節穩定民心、粉飾太平，嘗試提升返香港人對香港嘅歸屬感。商業電台六七暴動都元氣大傷，尤其播音員林彬(六七暴動期間林彬參演廣播劇《欲罷不能》、《大丈夫日記》，日日公開直屌匪。《欲罷不能》同之後另一個廣播劇節目《冷眼旁觀》就係《十八樓C座》前身)畀匪害死。香港之歌就係當年其中一首響應香港節嘅歌。1971年同1973年再搞過兩次，不過當時社會氣氛已經平靜曬，唔同69年，之後都冇再搞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.seewide.com/upload/article/201603/1456832178382104091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.seewide.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F201603%2F1456832178382104091.jpg&h=2df92cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/81/1e/86/811e86aefc25ea75467850ff0112364c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F81%2F1e%2F86%2F811e86aefc25ea75467850ff0112364c.jpg&h=078a191b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/1969年第一屆香港節沙田區裝飾-慶祝牌樓.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F1969%E5%B9%B4%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%B1%86%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AF%80%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%A3%9D%E9%A3%BE-%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D%E7%89%8C%E6%A8%93.png&h=c1c60b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkstmp.com/fd691209.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkstmp.com%2Ffd691209.JPG&h=46bae8d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkstmp.com/oldfoto05.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkstmp.com%2Foldfoto05.JPG&h=e5ef4d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gaahk.org.hk/wp-content/uploads/cover-b-225x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaahk.org.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fcover-b-225x300.jpg&h=12f59e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.grs.gov.hk/ws/online/GPM/filemanager/template/common/images/festival_of_hong_kong/po000095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grs.gov.hk%2Fws%2Fonline%2FGPM%2Ffilemanager%2Ftemplate%2Fcommon%2Fimages%2Ffestival_of_hong_kong%2Fpo000095.jpg&h=9a135d13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d99790e500609457284101ee86146899c0926113","tid":1263731,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:33:10.000Z","msg":"作曲鄺天培係商業電台開台初期營業部經理、中文節目部主任。除咗做幕後，亦都有參演過廣播劇同作過曲。作品有莫佩雯(秦煌老婆)〈勁草嬌花〉、尹芳玲〈薔薇之戀〉(1961年商台長篇廣播劇薔薇之戀主題曲)。連埋〈香港之歌〉，呢幾首歌都收入慶祝商業電台啟播十周年嘅《商台歌集第一輯》(1969)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/68f631fajw1eppc034hqgj20g80dsgnp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F68f631fajw1eppc034hqgj20g80dsgnp.jpg&h=63e5284f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cc720262713af4801dc4d5e9a63bd80ff113b8f","tid":1263731,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5722f9ed2965408ef06c6e16d752f16aac55f8bd","tid":1263731,"uid":217598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"我愛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2dcc50ab03da2e41a01c885b824a4459daf763","tid":1263731,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57344ed12cf37a8e65334e2a0cd91b471774dc8","tid":1263731,"uid":218729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"88c54abe1e829dc949091564980e464a2efec7bc","tid":1263731,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"1969年，六七暴動平息冇耐，港英搞咗個香港節穩定民心、粉飾太平，嘗試提升返香港人對香港嘅歸屬感。商業電台六七暴動都元氣大傷，尤其播音員林彬(六七暴動期間林彬參演廣播劇《欲罷不能》、《大丈夫日記》，日日公開直屌匪。《欲罷不能》同之後另一個廣播劇節目《冷眼旁觀》就係《十八樓C座》前身)畀匪害死。香港之歌就係當年其中一首響應香港節嘅歌。1971年同1973年再搞過兩次，不過當時社會氣氛已經平靜曬，唔同69年，之後都冇再搞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.seewide.com/upload/article/201603/1456832178382104091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.seewide.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F201603%2F1456832178382104091.jpg&h=2df92cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/81/1e/86/811e86aefc25ea75467850ff0112364c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F81%2F1e%2F86%2F811e86aefc25ea75467850ff0112364c.jpg&h=078a1